WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: ar

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
ذَرْنِي وَمَنْ خَلَقْتُ وَحِيدًا - 74:11
Leave Me with the one I created alone

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:10.400
وَجَعَلْتُ لَهُ مَالًا مَّمْدُودًا - 74:12
And to whom I granted extensive wealth

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:18.066
وَبَنِينَ شُهُودًا - 74:13 وَمَهَّدتُّ لَهُ تَمْهِيدًا - 74:14
And children present [with him]. And spread [everything] before him, easing [his life].

00:00:18.066 --> 00:00:32.899
ثُمَّ يَطْمَعُ أَنْ أَزِيدَ - 74:15 كَلَّا ۖ إِنَّهُ كَانَ لِآيَاتِنَا عَنِيدًا - 74:16
Then he desires that I should add more. No! Indeed, he has been toward Our verses obstinate.

00:00:32.900 --> 00:00:44.633
سَأُرْهِقُهُ صَعُودًا - 74:17 إِنَّهُ فَكَّرَ وَقَدَّرَ - 74:18 فَقُتِلَ كَيْفَ قَدَّرَ - 74:19
I will cover him with arduous torment. Indeed, he thought and deliberated. So may he be destroyed [for] how he deliberated.

00:00:44.633 --> 00:00:55.733
ثُمَّ قُتِلَ كَيْفَ قَدَّرَ - 74:20 ثُمَّ نَظَرَ - 74:21 ثُمَّ عَبَسَ وَبَسَرَ - 74:22
Then may he be destroyed [for] how he deliberated. Then he considered [again]; Then he frowned and scowled;

00:00:55.733 --> 00:01:08.366
ثُمَّ أَدْبَرَ وَاسْتَكْبَرَ - 74:23 فَقَالَ إِنْ هَٰذَا إِلَّا سِحْرٌ يُؤْثَرُ - 74:24
Then he turned back and was arrogant. And said, "This is not but magic imitated [from others].

00:01:08.366 --> 00:01:22.566
إِنْ هَٰذَا إِلَّا قَوْلُ الْبَشَرِ - 74:25 سَأُصْلِيهِ سَقَرَ - 74:26 وَمَا أَدْرَاكَ مَا سَقَرُ - 74:27
This is not but the word of a human being." I will drive him into Saqar. And what can make you know what is Saqar?

00:01:22.566 --> 00:01:32.499
لَا تُبْقِي وَلَا تَذَرُ - 74:28 لَوَّاحَةٌ لِّلْبَشَرِ - 74:29 عَلَيْهَا تِسْعَةَ عَشَرَ - 74:30
It lets nothing remain and leaves nothing [unburned], blackening the skins. Over it are nineteen [angels].

00:01:32.833 --> 00:01:37.166
أعوذ بالله من الشيطان الرجيم
I seek refuge in Allah from the accursed Satan.

00:01:37.166 --> 00:01:41.899
بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَٰنِ الرَّحِيمِ 
In the name of Allah, the Entirely Merciful, the Especially Merciful.

00:01:41.900 --> 00:01:54.133
يَا أَيُّهَا الْمُدَّثِّرُ - 74:1 قُمْ فَأَنذِرْ - 74:2 وَرَبَّكَ فَكَبِّرْ - 74:3
O you who covers himself [with a garment], arise and warn and your Lord glorify.

00:01:54.133 --> 00:02:04.366
وَثِيَابَكَ فَطَهِّرْ - 74:4 وَالرُّجْزَ فَاهْجُرْ - 74:5 وَلَا تَمْنُن تَسْتَكْثِرُ - 74:6
And your clothing purify. And uncleanliness avoid. And do not confer favor to acquire more.

00:02:04.366 --> 00:02:21.432
وَلِرَبِّكَ فَاصْبِرْ - 74:7 فَإِذَا نُقِرَ فِي النَّاقُورِ - 74:8 فَذَٰلِكَ يَوْمَئِذٍ يَوْمٌ عَسِيرٌ - 74:9
But for your Lord be patient. And when the trumpet is blown, that Day will be a difficult day.

00:02:21.433 --> 00:02:27.366
عَلَى الْكَافِرِينَ غَيْرُ يَسِيرٍ - 74:10 
For the disbelievers - not easy.

